verbose_text: TLR2 mRNA and TLR4 mRNA levels in DP-IBS and NDP-IBS patients were significantly higher than those in the control group (0.013 +/- 0.002, 0.009 +/- 0.003, and 0.006 +/- 0.002, resp., F = 5.018, P = 0.008; 0.012 +/- 0.002, 0.009 +/- 0.001, and 0.005 +/- 0.001, resp., F = 12.015, P = 0.000), and those in DP-IBS patients were significantly higher than those in NDP-IBS patients (P < 0.05) (XREF_FIG).
